# Internal planning + security context. NOT for the public repo.
# These carry the build roadmap, sales positioning, the Supabase project layout and the
# credential-hardening narrative (incl. an unrotated key and where it reaches). They are
# read by the agent from disk; nothing in the app imports them.
# Removing them here does NOT undo the exposure -- git history still holds every version.
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
plan.md
phase-b-execution-plan.md
loom-script.md
HARDENING-STATUS.md
